{"tid":542164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭稱不希望中美等國爆發貿易戰","createTime":"2018-01-27T08:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T01:18:59.000Z","uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"27f83694478439cfa64862c26ce6cbe7bd4ed513","tid":542164,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T08:19:19.000Z","msg":"在達沃斯出席論壇的行政長官林鄭月娥則表示，不希望看到中美等國爆發貿易戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/520505/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%8B%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F520505%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B8%258C%25E6%259C%259B%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0&d=c0D1ETolRcubLxqClEL4RDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=216dfcd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F520505%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B8%258C%25E6%259C%259B%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0&h=f6e2c26f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/520505/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%8B%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥在瑞士達沃斯經濟論壇上，被問到美國總統特朗普曾公開指中國侵犯美國知識產權等行為，中美一旦爆發貿易戰，香港會如何應對風險。她指，香港作為一個外向型經濟體，不願意見到任何貿易摩擦或貿易戰，但香港對貿易逆差並不陌生。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥引述自己在亞太經合會議與特朗普的對話，她表示美國最大的貿易順差，就是來自香港，每年310億美元，又說特朗普聽到之後似乎有點高興。林鄭月娥又指，中國仍是一個發展中國家，未來會有進步及改善，努力令貿易對所有人都變得更透明和公平。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1377571-20180127.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1377571-20180127.htm&d=c0D1ETolRcubLxqClEL4RDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=19317b89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1377571-20180127.htm&h=3117d348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1377571-20180127.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2c0e136dbc3bda647f087133a726806d863f34","tid":542164,"uid":37596,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T08:21:17.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥引述自己在亞太經合會議與特朗普的對話，她表示美國最大的貿易順差，就是來自香港，每年310億美元，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n當自己係國家元首,可以DQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5009eec678b60f78e75905bc7f6ad46e006544e","tid":542164,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T08:23:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e59d05950c1a1c290a5a0bd5c40433f2a767c1b","tid":542164,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T08:27:07.000Z","msg":"侵 你邊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354dd514278aaf97bad6868e8a432a1d1e847c51","tid":542164,"uid":33886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T08:29:55.000Z","msg":"又幾型棍子"},{"pid":"ce92516ff4cd11f5281d1833c6bc0579b949d943","tid":542164,"uid":3773,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T08:31:40.000Z","msg":"輪到你話事咩？性病傀儡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2911d95c6589b17fb263825267ec82a0d2da69e","tid":542164,"uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":12,"sco